author: Benzilla
text:
Feeling emotional today... It's the end of an era for Benzilla Studios. 

My series was a great journey, thank you all so much for everything, y'all don't understand how much I appreciate you guys for your support.

author: Benzilla
text:
We'll see what happens when that day comes. Until then, it's time for you guys to get to know actual real Ben. 

Let's get this party started. Always believe in yourselves and Never Stop Dreaming. Love you guys. ❤️🙏

author: Benzilla
text:
2022 is the year of the journey, it will continue as we grow and learn from whatever we go through. 

I don't know when my next big series will come, but when it does, I will be ready to tell it and maybe top my "BenzillaVerse Saga" Storyline.

author: Benzilla
text:
Looking forward to sharing my actual real life with you guys. Also growing the Donut Show Cinematic Universe with Mandy Rose and Sonya Deville, big things coming from us. 

My videos of "Real life" has been part of the story and not actually real.
